{"tid":1360870,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CCTVB新聞真正幕後黑手，總監「黃淑明」","createTime":"2019-07-24T12:48:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T03:18:21.000Z","uid":183666,"like":223,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"c837797c5e84b0ce1fcef58b10889aa09aea36ca","tid":1360870,"uid":183666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:48:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cwHMwQT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcwHMwQT.png&h=947bcfe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幕後黑手都係「花哥」？<br />\n<br />\n「花哥的確事事關心。」A 回顧自己尚在無線，袁志偉＊的確宵旰憂勤，事無大小事事過問，務使下屬不敢逾越。<br />\n<br />\n（註：「我好似冇聽過同事叫佢袁生，大家都叫佢花哥。。。」）<br />\n<br />\n過去無線有一獨特風氣，只可意會不可言傳 － 每逢「花哥」外遊，就是無線新聞「小陽春」的時候。「佢唔喺度就作反，啲報道即刻 sharp 左好多。有時佢番嚟會追究，但好多時佢冇為意到就算。」<br />\n<br />\n不過「小陽春」的日子已愈來愈少，近乎曇花一現。畢竟袁志偉已升上管理層，管不了那麼多。「好多時佢未出聲，下面嘅人（總監、經理、編輯、採主）早已經出手干預。」<br />\n<br />\nA 說在傘運期間，「唔乖」的同事都不得落場採訪傘運。其中一人更被調往朝早五點更 － 做《香港早晨》。「確保左係『安全』嘅記者出去做 live，唔會亂講嘢。」<br />\n<br />\n網絡不時重提民建聯總幹事陸漢德，A 澄清他既無實權，也早已離開無線。現在是由黃淑明接任袁志偉升遷而留下的總監位置。<br />\n<br />\n黃淑明既掌管所有稿件；也監督所有影片。在她治下影片的剪輯和長度，更嚴重地向建制靠攏。<br />\n<br />\nA 說：「有啲時候花哥比明姐更會聆聽同事；明姐係鐵板一塊。以前審查尚有些少機會突圍；而家審查已經制度化，明姐要滴水不漏。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/究竟-TVB-發生咩事-無線的問題並非僅僅染紅-前員工-籲勿誤中副車傷害有心人/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F-TVB-%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E5%92%A9%E4%BA%8B-%E7%84%A1%E7%B7%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E4%B8%A6%E9%9D%9E%E5%83%85%E5%83%85%E6%9F%93%E7%B4%85-%E5%89%8D%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5-%E7%B1%B2%E5%8B%BF%E8%AA%A4%E4%B8%AD%E5%89%AF%E8%BB%8A%E5%82%B7%E5%AE%B3%E6%9C%89%E5%BF%83%E4%BA%BA%2F&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9ZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=d5605621\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F-TVB-%E7%99%BC%E7%94%9F%E5%92%A9%E4%BA%8B-%E7%84%A1%E7%B7%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C%E4%B8%A6%E9%9D%9E%E5%83%85%E5%83%85%E6%9F%93%E7%B4%85-%E5%89%8D%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5-%E7%B1%B2%E5%8B%BF%E8%AA%A4%E4%B8%AD%E5%89%AF%E8%BB%8A%E5%82%B7%E5%AE%B3%E6%9C%89%E5%BF%83%E4%BA%BA%2F&h=5e8eb14a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/究竟-TVB-發生咩事-無線的問題並非僅僅染紅-前員工-籲勿誤中副車傷害有心人/</a>"},{"pid":"6095316e04aae54857e175e7442db318379ee85d","tid":1360870,"uid":37596,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:49:50.000Z","msg":"連登仔出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bfba5aa401583da788cf3a1747fb32b233915f","tid":1360870,"uid":183666,"like":96,"dislike":0,"score":96,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0YBmkNs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0YBmkNs.jpg&h=2ae78ec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃淑明 <br />\n1987年畢業於樂善堂余近卿中學 <br />\n1990年畢業於浸會大學前身浸會學院傳理系 <br />\n現職無綫新聞部總監"},{"pid":"2434440505a75cba3ac3fd877f470166c747f7e7","tid":1360870,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:56:20.000Z","msg":"唔夠膽講老細金主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dca6e1e254580b6dfa38ec5a6c4d3ae30daad003","tid":1360870,"uid":183666,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:08:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dEmp249.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdEmp249.jpg&h=adeb22ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/355810/逃犯條例-tvb非新聞部員工譴責無綫新聞偏頗-新聞不是工具/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F355810%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-tvb%E9%9D%9E%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E9%83%A8%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%81%8F%E9%A0%97-%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E5%B7%A5%E5%85%B7%2F&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9ZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=982df37e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/355810/逃犯條例-tvb非新聞部員工譴責無綫新聞偏頗-新聞不是工具/</a>"},{"pid":"75b9d2bb480ecff48225e17ef98d9eeca273b915","tid":1360870,"uid":229289,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:10:09.000Z","msg":"清算理陷家鏟"},{"pid":"06c6dd080df4c6ad39a8c9052bdb11dc4ccb47ae","tid":1360870,"uid":183666,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"6095316e04aae54857e175e7442db318379ee85d","tid":1360870,"uid":37596,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:49:50.000Z","msg":"連登仔出動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:12:04.000Z","msg":"連登仔剩係知道袁志偉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5622e1e0ac75e2072587b5cb32dbe5e960c339dc","tid":1360870,"uid":126648,"like":33,"dislike":12,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:12:14.000Z","msg":"女人話事都係仆街"},{"pid":"225c6dfa02e085a28be181d1b0cd7846de487275","tid":1360870,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:14:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c19e418659eb78800eabd530ed1d02f53b714889","tid":1360870,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:28:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8083c4f1fb69ad1adcead1d1cbf5551b2b5a6a92","tid":1360870,"uid":129134,"like":85,"dislike":0,"score":85,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:35:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/82wQYNu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F82wQYNu.jpg&h=f4173642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有人爆大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e5d96650f8813ee16000b0b0b35a5825e51857df","tid":1360870,"uid":183666,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:46:30.000Z","msg":"雨傘革命之TVB的河蟹與清算<br />\n<a href=\"https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/雨傘革命之TVB的河蟹與清算#cite_note-20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.org%2Fzh%2Fwiki%2F%E9%9B%A8%E5%82%98%E9%9D%A9%E5%91%BD%E4%B9%8BTVB%E7%9A%84%E6%B2%B3%E8%9F%B9%E8%88%87%E6%B8%85%E7%AE%97%23cite_note-20&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9ZMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=c0fc4436\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://evchk.wikia.org/zh/wiki/雨傘革命之TVB的河蟹與清算#cite_note-20</a><br />\n<br />\n新聞組清算開始<br />\n<br />\n2014年11月上旬，TVB急不及待進行秋後算帳。無綫新聞部經理<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黃淑明</strong></span>向員工發內部電郵，內容指負責「暗角打鑊」的採訪主任何永康，被調職為「首席資料搜集員」，揚言是希望可更好地支援不同的新聞專題環節。<br />\n<br />\n「暗角七警」河蟹前報導獲獎<br />\n<br />\n2015年6月下旬，「暗角七警」事件發生二百多天後，無綫新聞部憑著《六點半新聞報道》播出的「暗角七警」及「龍和道示威」報道，勇奪第55屆蒙地卡羅國際電視節最佳電視新聞獎。<br />\n<br />\n獲獎的是被袁志偉河蟹前的版本。評判指出，片段能夠勇奪得獎項，全因報道全面、客觀、中立、專業，以及有勇氣報道社會的不公義，所以獲得評委高度評價。更有趣的是有關奪獎的相關報道，報喜的竟不是新聞部，而是6月22日晚上播出的《東張西望》。<br />\n<br />\n據悉無綫內部有記者認為，高層一方面出手打壓報道，將「拳打腳踢」的旁述刪走，但又以此報道參賽，明言「睇唔過眼」，而領獎者更是當時支持新聞部總監袁志偉刪走有關旁述的新聞部經理<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黃淑明</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n有網民直斥：「個獎唔屬於TVB 及袁生，係屬於TVB新聞部有良心嘅前員工及現職員工！」另外亦有網民嘆息所有功臣已被逼離開TVB。"},{"pid":"c4609c80b29e0fc2ed4897eaf7699cf403a35555","tid":1360870,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ca31b5a2d80ff82c6e77238e2e520cfadde974","tid":1360870,"uid":129134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:49:07.000Z","msg":"鬼鼠TVB新聞部隱藏良心員工梁凱寧同褚簡寧評論壽終正寢片段<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1358198/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1358198/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n屌柒TVB - 罷買「日本獅王、大班/榮華月餅、御藥堂、必理痛」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1357086/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1357086/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\nTVB 新聞部跟機 (有員工證)<br />\n<a href=\"https://li